-- RWE Won’t Build More Nuclear Power Stations, Sueddeutsche Says
-- B y   J e f f   B l a c k
-- 2012-06-17T15:43:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-17/rwe-won-t-build-more-nuclear-power-stations-sueddeutsche-says.html
RWE AG (RWE)  decided not to build any more
nuclear power stations abroad following Germany’s exit from
atomic energy,  Sueddeutsche Zeitung  reported, citing unnamed
people familiar with the company’s strategy.  RWE is planning to expand its activities in solar energy,
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jeff Black in Frankfurt at 
